description:
Marcus Barney aka Him 500 has established himself as one of the most dangerous men online teaching things that you can’t Google. His journey from working at a cell phone store, to becoming a multi-millionaire in a few years has become legendary. On episode 115, we sat down with Marcus for a powerful conversation. He outlined strategies on how to turn credit into cash and how to leverage both personal and business credit to build wealth. We went in-depth on actionable items and even discussed topics that have the potential to turn anyone into a millionaire.
